WEBVTT

00:00:00.910 --> 00:00:02.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:01:08.750 --> 00:01:14.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:01:31.290 --> 00:01:35.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>THE WORLD DREAMS</b></Default>

00:01:35.950 --> 00:01:38.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ distant
concert music playing]</b></Default>

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mai singing
Japanese rock song]</b></Default>

00:02:13.870 --> 00:02:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[song ends]</b></Default>

00:02:27.409 --> 00:02:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Thank you all</i>
<i>for coming tonight.</i></b></Default>

00:02:29.330 --> 00:02:31.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I have an important</i>
<i>announcement to share with you.</i></b></Default>

00:02:32.250 --> 00:02:33.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I'm sure some of you have</i></b></Default>

00:02:33.370 --> 00:02:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>already realized this</i>
<i>by now, but...</i></b></Default>

00:02:36.500 --> 00:02:37.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>truth is</b></Default>

00:02:37.949 --> 00:02:40.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I am really Touko Kirishima.</i></b></Default>

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:45.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:02:49.039 --> 00:02:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>And now</b></Default>

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:51.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>here's one more song!</i></b></Default>

00:02:51.870 --> 00:02:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ gentle music playing]</b></Default>

00:03:00.659 --> 00:03:01.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[line ringing]</b></Default>

00:03:04.199 --> 00:03:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Hello, Akagi here.</i></b></Default>

00:03:06.500 --> 00:03:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, it's Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:03:08.580 --> 00:03:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I see you later today?</b></Default>

00:03:16.159 --> 00:03:18.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans softly]</b></Default>

00:03:18.659 --> 00:03:20.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 25TH</b></Default>

00:03:20.159 --> 00:03:21.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning, Mai.</b></Default>

00:03:22.539 --> 00:03:25.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah! Did I say something
strange in my sleep?</b></Default>

00:03:25.870 --> 00:03:28.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What were you and Akagi
doing together in your dream?</b></Default>

00:03:28.500 --> 00:03:31.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was just giving her a call</b></Default>

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:34.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, your smartphone?
Are you sure?</b></Default>

00:03:34.289 --> 00:03:36.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Yeah.
-Hmm.</b></Default>

00:03:36.199 --> 00:03:37.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is a strange dream.</b></Default>

00:03:37.699 --> 00:03:39.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I was
at a music festival</b></Default>

00:03:39.870 --> 00:03:41.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and for some reason</b></Default>

00:03:41.620 --> 00:03:43.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a Touko Kirishima song.</b></Default>

00:03:43.580 --> 00:03:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You even claimed
to be Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:03:45.580 --> 00:03:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in front of everyone.</b></Default>

00:03:47.909 --> 00:03:50.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think it's another one
of those prophetic dreams</b></Default>

00:03:50.250 --> 00:03:51.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's been going around?</b></Default>

00:03:51.789 --> 00:03:52.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:03:52.830 --> 00:03:54.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was eerily realistic.</b></Default>

00:03:54.949 --> 00:03:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Either way</b></Default>

00:03:56.330 --> 00:03:58.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't have any plans
to perform at a music festival.</b></Default>

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And me being Touko Kirishima
isn't even possible.</b></Default>

00:04:02.699 --> 00:04:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning, you two!</b></Default>

00:04:04.199 --> 00:04:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning to you.</b></Default>

00:04:06.289 --> 00:04:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Mai!</b></Default>

00:04:07.409 --> 00:04:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's something
I forgot to tell you yesterday</b></Default>

00:04:09.949 --> 00:04:12.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but we received
an unusual offer.</b></Default>

00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:14.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's for
a music-related project.</b></Default>

00:04:14.699 --> 00:04:15.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasp softly]</b></Default>

00:04:16.790 --> 00:04:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it an offer for me to perform
at an upcoming music festival?</b></Default>

00:04:20.449 --> 00:04:22.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, how did you figure that out?</b></Default>

00:04:24.660 --> 00:04:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] <i>According to Ryoko</b></Default>

00:04:26.449 --> 00:04:29.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>the music festival is going</i>
<i>to be held on 1st April.</i></b></Default>

00:04:29.949 --> 00:04:32.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>That's still</i>
<i>quite a while from now.</i></b></Default>

00:04:32.250 --> 00:04:34.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] <i>The band that performed</i>
<i>with me in the movie</i></b></Default>

00:04:34.199 --> 00:04:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>that came out last month</i></b></Default>

00:04:35.620 --> 00:04:37.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>is inviting me</i>
<i>to one of their gigs</i></b></Default>

00:04:37.160 --> 00:04:38.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>as a guest vocalist, I guess.</i></b></Default>

00:04:39.870 --> 00:04:42.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So then</b></Default>

00:04:42.410 --> 00:04:43.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll have to accept.</b></Default>

00:04:43.660 --> 00:04:46.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do feel obliged
to help them out after all.</b></Default>

00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:48.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I guess that means
we're one step closer</b></Default>

00:04:48.790 --> 00:04:50.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to that future in my dream.</b></Default>

00:04:50.910 --> 00:04:52.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, maybe.</b></Default>

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:54.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>AlI I have to do now
is reveal to everyone</b></Default>

00:04:54.290 --> 00:04:55.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Touko Kirishima, right?</b></Default>

00:04:55.910 --> 00:04:57.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess so.</b></Default>

00:04:57.329 --> 00:05:00.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that means I'm gonna have
to buy a smartphone too.</b></Default>

00:05:01.290 --> 00:05:02.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'm home.
-[door closes]</b></Default>

00:05:02.910 --> 00:05:04.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You're super late, Big Brother.
-[news playing on TV]</b></Default>

00:05:04.699 --> 00:05:05.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Nasuno purring]</b></Default>

00:05:05.699 --> 00:05:08.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Considering I'm coming back
from a date, I'd say I'm early.</b></Default>

00:05:08.750 --> 00:05:09.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NEWS ANCHOR]
<i>There have been reports</i></b></Default>

00:05:09.750 --> 00:05:10.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>of people having difficulties</i></b></Default>

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:13.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>accessing several popular</i>
<i>social media services.</i></b></Default>

00:05:13.790 --> 00:05:14.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>LARGE-SCALE NATIONWIDE
COMMUNICATION FAILURE</b></Default>

00:05:14.790 --> 00:05:15.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>The reason for this incident</i></b></Default>

00:05:15.790 --> 00:05:16.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>is believed</i>
<i>to be server flooding</i></b></Default>

00:05:16.790 --> 00:05:18.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>from simultaneous posts</i></b></Default>

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:20.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>with a #Dreaming</i>
<i>currently viral...</i></b></Default>

00:05:20.500 --> 00:05:22.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Dreaming tag again?</b></Default>

00:05:22.290 --> 00:05:24.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[news continues indistinctly]</b></Default>

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:26.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you happen
to see a dream too, Kaede?</b></Default>

00:05:27.079 --> 00:05:28.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did.</b></Default>

00:05:29.370 --> 00:05:31.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was it such
an embarrassing dream</b></Default>

00:05:31.290 --> 00:05:32.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you don't want
to talk about it?</b></Default>

00:05:32.910 --> 00:05:35.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not that it was
embarrassing, but--</b></Default>

00:05:35.160 --> 00:05:36.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But what?</b></Default>

00:05:36.750 --> 00:05:39.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I dreamed that
I was back to my other self.</b></Default>

00:05:39.620 --> 00:05:41.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Me and Nasuno were here</b></Default>

00:05:41.540 --> 00:05:43.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>waiting for you to come home.</b></Default>

00:05:44.870 --> 00:05:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, surely
that wouldn't come true.</b></Default>

00:05:47.079 --> 00:05:49.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there something on your mind
that would cause you to relapse?</b></Default>

00:05:50.870 --> 00:05:52.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My future.</b></Default>

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:54.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's actually a healthy thing
to have on your mind.</b></Default>

00:05:55.500 --> 00:05:57.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'm going to apply to college.
-[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:05:58.790 --> 00:06:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm still not very comfortable
in places with a lot of people.</b></Default>

00:06:02.079 --> 00:06:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Komi told me
that her first choice school</b></Default>

00:06:04.329 --> 00:06:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was the university you go to.</b></Default>

00:06:06.579 --> 00:06:07.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I thought about it.</b></Default>

00:06:07.910 --> 00:06:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if Komi's there</b></Default>

00:06:11.790 --> 00:06:12.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that bad?</b></Default>

00:06:13.620 --> 00:06:15.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think so.</b></Default>

00:06:15.160 --> 00:06:16.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean</b></Default>

00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the same university as Mai.
So I get it.</b></Default>

00:06:19.660 --> 00:06:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, are you good on time?</b></Default>

00:06:21.449 --> 00:06:23.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your shift
starts at 6:00, right?</b></Default>

00:06:23.660 --> 00:06:24.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

00:06:25.829 --> 00:06:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Later, Big Bro.</b></Default>

00:06:29.949 --> 00:06:31.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede's dream, huh?</b></Default>

00:06:37.199 --> 00:06:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[typing]</b></Default>

00:06:38.829 --> 00:06:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I DREAMED I WAS TALKING ABOUT
BREAKING UP WITH MY BOYFRIEND.</b></Default>

00:06:40.579 --> 00:06:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A DREAM OF GETTING INTO COLLEGE.</b></Default>

00:06:41.620 --> 00:06:42.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>VIEWING CHERRY BLOSSOMS
AT NIGHT.</b></Default>

00:06:46.410 --> 00:06:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:06:51.949 --> 00:06:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[line ringing]</b></Default>

00:06:56.500 --> 00:06:57.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] <i>Hello.</i></b></Default>

00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:06:59.329 --> 00:07:01.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this the correct number
for Miss Akagi?</b></Default>

00:07:01.500 --> 00:07:03.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Uh-oh, Azusagawa?</i></b></Default>

00:07:04.250 --> 00:07:05.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
<i>Sorry to call out of the blue</i></b></Default>

00:07:05.410 --> 00:07:06.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>on Christmas night.</i></b></Default>

00:07:06.410 --> 00:07:09.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who gave you my number?</b></Default>

00:07:09.250 --> 00:07:10.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Well</b></Default>

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I saw it in my dream</i></b></Default>

00:07:12.699 --> 00:07:14.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>because I dialed</i>
<i>your number in it.</i></b></Default>

00:07:14.750 --> 00:07:15.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So then</b></Default>

00:07:15.829 --> 00:07:17.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I decided to call
this number to see</b></Default>

00:07:17.540 --> 00:07:19.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if it really belonged to you.</b></Default>

00:07:19.250 --> 00:07:20.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry for the sudden call.</b></Default>

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Don't worry about it.</i></b></Default>

00:07:22.870 --> 00:07:25.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's something I wanted
to talk to you about as well.</b></Default>

00:07:25.750 --> 00:07:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Can it be that</i>
<i>you also had a dream?</i></b></Default>

00:07:28.370 --> 00:07:29.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

00:07:29.500 --> 00:07:32.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I also had a dream where
I received a call from you.</b></Default>

00:07:32.250 --> 00:07:34.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said, "Can I see you later?"</b></Default>

00:07:34.370 --> 00:07:37.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>So, a dream of</i>
<i>the same day as the one I saw.</i></b></Default>

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] <i>Hey, Azusagawa...</i></b></Default>

00:07:40.370 --> 00:07:41.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think</b></Default>

00:07:41.370 --> 00:07:43.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I may have figured out
what the dream was about.</b></Default>

00:07:43.910 --> 00:07:45.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, really?</b></Default>

00:07:45.500 --> 00:07:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Actually</b></Default>

00:07:46.750 --> 00:07:48.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>that dream is...</i></b></Default>

00:07:48.410 --> 00:07:49.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 28TH - SHONAN PERSONAL
INSTRUCTION CRAM SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:07:49.750 --> 00:07:52.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YAMADA] Mr. Sakuta, is it cool
if I skip today's class?</b></Default>

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:55.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me why</b></Default>

00:07:55.579 --> 00:07:58.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a dream
on the night of Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:07:58.829 --> 00:07:59.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind?</b></Default>

00:08:03.040 --> 00:08:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A dream where I'm on a date
with Yoshiwa at Enoshima.</b></Default>

00:08:05.949 --> 00:08:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, that's pretty dreamy.</b></Default>

00:08:07.579 --> 00:08:09.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We ate sardine bowls together.</b></Default>

00:08:09.449 --> 00:08:11.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She hand-fed me
some soft serve ice cream</b></Default>

00:08:11.699 --> 00:08:13.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then we held hands.</b></Default>

00:08:13.500 --> 00:08:15.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So basically</b></Default>

00:08:15.750 --> 00:08:18.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you want to skip class because
you feel awkward seeing Yoshiwa?</b></Default>

00:08:18.370 --> 00:08:19.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-huh.</b></Default>

00:08:19.370 --> 00:08:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yamada.
Didn't you have the hots</b></Default>

00:08:21.329 --> 00:08:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Himeji until recently?</b></Default>

00:08:23.079 --> 00:08:24.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps, sighs]</b></Default>

00:08:24.829 --> 00:08:26.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bumped into Himeji
at the train station</b></Default>

00:08:26.750 --> 00:08:28.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the evening of Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:08:28.540 --> 00:08:29.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said something like</b></Default>

00:08:29.660 --> 00:08:32.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I'm sorry if I gave you
the wrong idea until now."</b></Default>

00:08:32.450 --> 00:08:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on, Yamada.
I thought you didn't believe</b></Default>

00:08:34.830 --> 00:08:37.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in occult stories and stuff
like the Dreaming tag.</b></Default>

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course</b></Default>

00:08:38.950 --> 00:08:41.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Yoshiwa might have had
the same dream I did, you know?</b></Default>

00:08:41.700 --> 00:08:43.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been happening to everyone!
And, uh...</b></Default>

00:08:45.659 --> 00:08:47.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:08:50.450 --> 00:08:53.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That pretty much confirms
she had the same dream.</b></Default>

00:08:53.500 --> 00:08:57.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But regardless, everyone keeps
talking about dreams lately.</b></Default>

00:08:57.789 --> 00:09:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 3RD</b></Default>

00:09:00.330 --> 00:09:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>HAPPY NEW YEAR</b></Default>

00:09:01.330 --> 00:09:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

00:09:02.330 --> 00:09:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FATHER] No, I really
thought that was a mochi.</b></Default>

00:09:03.830 --> 00:09:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You understand?
-[SAKUTA] That's lame.</b></Default>

00:09:05.909 --> 00:09:07.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My dear</b></Default>

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>thank you again
for sending us the fish cakes.</b></Default>

00:09:09.370 --> 00:09:11.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on. I thought those
were under my name, though.</b></Default>

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Mai was the one who thought
of sending it, right?</b></Default>

00:09:15.580 --> 00:09:18.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gotta hand it to you, Mom.
You have us figured out.</b></Default>

00:09:18.659 --> 00:09:20.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>We'll be back</i>
<i>after a brief news update</i>.</b></Default>

00:09:20.789 --> 00:09:21.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>GOGOICHI SQUARE
NEW YEAR SPECIAL</b></Default>

00:09:21.830 --> 00:09:22.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>This just in.</i></b></Default>

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Before dawn yesterday</b></Default>

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>for walking around</i>
<i>bending license plates on cars</b></Default>

00:09:27.620 --> 00:09:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>in a residential district</i>
<i>of Yokohama.</i></b></Default>

00:09:30.289 --> 00:09:32.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>During police investigation</b></Default>

00:09:32.289 --> 00:09:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>"I had a dream that I still</i>
<i>wasn't employed in April</b></Default>

00:09:34.450 --> 00:09:36.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>and I did it because</i>
<i>I was feeling irritated</i></b></Default>

00:09:37.039 --> 00:09:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>and annoyed."</i>
<i>The police are...</i></b></Default>

00:09:38.450 --> 00:09:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a rather
strange incident.</b></Default>

00:09:40.580 --> 00:09:41.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I agree.</b></Default>

00:09:41.620 --> 00:09:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, Mai</b></Default>

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:45.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you remember what kind of
dream you had on Christmas Eve?</b></Default>

00:09:46.330 --> 00:09:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I actually didn't have one.</b></Default>

00:09:48.620 --> 00:09:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, you didn't?</b></Default>

00:09:50.620 --> 00:09:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MOTHER] Mai</b></Default>

00:09:52.159 --> 00:09:53.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is this year.</b></Default>

00:09:53.159 --> 00:09:54.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will you be wearing a kimono?</b></Default>

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:57.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, my mother
suddenly visited me yesterday</b></Default>

00:09:57.909 --> 00:10:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she left one for me</b></Default>

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow. So pretty.</b></Default>

00:10:02.409 --> 00:10:04.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure it'll look great
on you, Mai.</b></Default>

00:10:04.250 --> 00:10:06.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's truly a beautiful design.</b></Default>

00:10:06.620 --> 00:10:08.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm looking forward to
Kaede turning 20.</b></Default>

00:10:09.409 --> 00:10:11.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We still have a while
before that, Mom.</b></Default>

00:10:11.870 --> 00:10:13.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just three more years, huh?</b></Default>

00:10:13.789 --> 00:10:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, that's still a ways to go.</b></Default>

00:10:15.950 --> 00:10:18.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FATHER] <i>But those three years</i>
<i>will fly by before you know it.</i></b></Default>

00:10:19.870 --> 00:10:22.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah. I had adream
on Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:24.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were performing
at a concert hall in Yokohama.</b></Default>

00:10:25.159 --> 00:10:26.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of the girls
in Sweet Bullet even said</b></Default>

00:10:26.870 --> 00:10:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that they had
the same dream too.</b></Default>

00:10:28.659 --> 00:10:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I see.</b></Default>

00:10:29.830 --> 00:10:31.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to bother you
on your break.</b></Default>

00:10:31.409 --> 00:10:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Later.</b></Default>

00:10:32.950 --> 00:10:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Are you starting
to get worried</b></Default>

00:10:34.450 --> 00:10:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I didn't have a dream?</b></Default>

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mostly because
you're the only one</b></Default>

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>close to me that didn't.</b></Default>

00:10:38.950 --> 00:10:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you think
we should be more worried</b></Default>

00:10:40.700 --> 00:10:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about you having all these
strange dreams instead?</b></Default>

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the Santa Claus
that only you can see</b></Default>

00:10:45.659 --> 00:10:47.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is even more worrying.</b></Default>

00:10:47.370 --> 00:10:50.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, if this is really
about not having a dream</b></Default>

00:10:50.539 --> 00:10:52.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can't you say the same
for your parents?</b></Default>

00:10:52.409 --> 00:10:54.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but they're
full grown adults.</b></Default>

00:10:54.330 --> 00:10:56.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're nowhere
near pubescent age.</b></Default>

00:10:56.450 --> 00:10:58.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then perhaps my time
of going through puberty</b></Default>

00:10:58.580 --> 00:10:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is over now.</b></Default>

00:10:59.620 --> 00:11:02.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are actually
really mature after all.</b></Default>

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:04.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should try
growing up soon too, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:11:04.620 --> 00:11:06.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That way, you wouldn't
have to be worried</b></Default>

00:11:06.370 --> 00:11:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about puberty syndrome
all the time.</b></Default>

00:11:09.039 --> 00:11:11.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 5TH</b></Default>

00:11:11.159 --> 00:11:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, good morning
to you, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:11:14.370 --> 00:11:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, come on, sir, you should
be way more surprised.</b></Default>

00:11:18.789 --> 00:11:20.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Normally this would be
where you ask</b></Default>

00:11:20.539 --> 00:11:22.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"What are you doing here?"
You know.</b></Default>

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:24.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you started
working here, right?</b></Default>

00:11:24.159 --> 00:11:25.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can tell by looking.</b></Default>

00:11:25.700 --> 00:11:26.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Boo.</b></Default>

00:11:26.789 --> 00:11:27.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're no fun.</b></Default>

00:11:27.950 --> 00:11:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, by the way, Himeji</b></Default>

00:11:30.580 --> 00:11:32.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>did you have a dream
on Christmas Eve?</b></Default>

00:11:32.370 --> 00:11:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I did.</b></Default>

00:11:33.830 --> 00:11:35.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I dreamt that I met up
with some friends</b></Default>

00:11:35.659 --> 00:11:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hang out in Enoshima.</b></Default>

00:11:36.789 --> 00:11:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By any chance</b></Default>

00:11:37.870 --> 00:11:40.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you didn't happen to see Yamada
there too, did you?</b></Default>

00:11:40.250 --> 00:11:41.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I did, actually.</b></Default>

00:11:41.750 --> 00:11:43.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think he was on a date
with Yoshiwa.</b></Default>

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was in love with me
not too long ago.</b></Default>

00:11:46.159 --> 00:11:48.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just how terrible
can that boy be?</b></Default>

00:11:48.159 --> 00:11:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, by the way</b></Default>

00:11:49.659 --> 00:11:51.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>did you know
about this, Mr. Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone is saying that</b></Default>

00:11:53.370 --> 00:11:56.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai Sakurajima
is Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:11:56.159 --> 00:11:58.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are over 5</b></Default>

00:11:58.750 --> 00:12:02.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I'd say 5</b></Default>

00:12:02.159 --> 00:12:03.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grumbling]</b></Default>

00:12:03.330 --> 00:12:04.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] What is it?</b></Default>

00:12:04.409 --> 00:12:06.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have a complaint
against me or something?</b></Default>

00:12:06.700 --> 00:12:07.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not it.</b></Default>

00:12:08.039 --> 00:12:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just thought I'd talk to you
about #Dreaming.</b></Default>

00:12:10.830 --> 00:12:13.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you had a dream on the night
of Christmas Eve too?</b></Default>

00:12:14.289 --> 00:12:16.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like I think everyone did.</b></Default>

00:12:16.159 --> 00:12:17.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay</b></Default>

00:12:17.250 --> 00:12:20.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so did you see Mai's disclosure
during the music festival</b></Default>

00:12:20.120 --> 00:12:21.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in your dream as well?</b></Default>

00:12:21.409 --> 00:12:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, it wasn't that.</b></Default>

00:12:22.830 --> 00:12:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then what did you see?</b></Default>

00:12:24.080 --> 00:12:26.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, for some reason</b></Default>

00:12:26.330 --> 00:12:28.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>took place a lot earlier
than April 1st.</b></Default>

00:12:29.000 --> 00:12:31.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And in my dream</b></Default>

00:12:31.539 --> 00:12:34.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakurajima holds
a "police chief for a day" event</b></Default>

00:12:34.289 --> 00:12:36.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at Fujisawa Police Station.</b></Default>

00:12:36.159 --> 00:12:38.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At that event</b></Default>

00:12:38.200 --> 00:12:40.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>falls unconscious</b></Default>

00:12:40.789 --> 00:12:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I saw.</b></Default>

00:12:42.659 --> 00:12:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The news said she got crushed
by falling equipment</b></Default>

00:12:45.330 --> 00:12:47.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and was rushed
straight to the hospital.</b></Default>

00:12:47.330 --> 00:12:48.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:12:48.700 --> 00:12:49.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then?</b></Default>

00:12:49.789 --> 00:12:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't know what happened
to her afterwards, do you?</b></Default>

00:12:52.370 --> 00:12:53.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As far as I know</b></Default>

00:12:53.870 --> 00:12:56.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by April 9th</b></Default>

00:12:56.200 --> 00:12:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of her regaining consciousness.</b></Default>

00:12:57.830 --> 00:13:00.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Are you saying
you experienced a dream</b></Default>

00:13:00.409 --> 00:13:01.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>spending all those days?</b></Default>

00:13:01.909 --> 00:13:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not really that many days.</b></Default>

00:13:03.950 --> 00:13:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way you saw every day</b></Default>

00:13:05.580 --> 00:13:07.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>between Christmas Eve
and April 9th, right?</b></Default>

00:13:08.039 --> 00:13:09.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what if I did?</b></Default>

00:13:09.450 --> 00:13:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This time around, it's not like
I was repeating the same day</b></Default>

00:13:12.200 --> 00:13:13.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over and over again.</b></Default>

00:13:13.250 --> 00:13:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't tell me because
you're a few months away</b></Default>

00:13:15.620 --> 00:13:16.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from graduating high school</b></Default>

00:13:16.950 --> 00:13:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're worried about
making friends in college.</b></Default>

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:21.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you were
feeling uneasy, huh?</b></Default>

00:13:21.159 --> 00:13:23.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, just shut up, will you?</b></Default>

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:26.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I guess I should thank you.</b></Default>

00:13:26.500 --> 00:13:27.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really saved me.</b></Default>

00:13:27.870 --> 00:13:30.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, well</b></Default>

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Buy me a Mont Blanc
sometime, okay?</b></Default>

00:13:35.039 --> 00:13:36.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FIND TOUKO KIRISHIMA
MAI-SAN IS IN DANGER!</b></Default>

00:13:37.200 --> 00:13:40.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Geez. Now I'm eve
more confused than ever.</b></Default>

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:13:43.080 --> 00:13:44.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 6TH</b></Default>

00:13:44.080 --> 00:13:45.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] With all this
Touko Kirishima stuff</b></Default>

00:13:45.620 --> 00:13:47.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if Azusagawa
knows her identity.</b></Default>

00:13:47.909 --> 00:13:50.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] Of course. He would
if he's your boyfriend.</b></Default>

00:13:50.789 --> 00:13:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Happy New Year, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:13:52.620 --> 00:13:54.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Happy New Year wishes
to you as well.</b></Default>

00:13:54.830 --> 00:13:55.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good luck.</b></Default>

00:13:56.200 --> 00:13:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope the coming year
brings you fortune.</b></Default>

00:13:58.159 --> 00:13:59.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Brighten up!</b></Default>

00:13:59.500 --> 00:14:01.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I have been disciplined
to greet people properly</b></Default>

00:14:01.750 --> 00:14:02.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the most incredible</b></Default>

00:14:02.789 --> 00:14:04.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and cutest girlfriend
in the world.</b></Default>

00:14:06.450 --> 00:14:07.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] Oh, yeah</b></Default>

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:09.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the way</b></Default>

00:14:09.409 --> 00:14:10.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who is the cutest in the world</b></Default>

00:14:11.250 --> 00:14:13.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are all those
Touko Kirishima rumors real?</b></Default>

00:14:13.750 --> 00:14:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That thing people are hyping up
on social media</b></Default>

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:17.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as group prognostication?</b></Default>

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:19.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You seriously think people
seeing their futures and dreams</b></Default>

00:14:20.039 --> 00:14:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is a real thing?</b></Default>

00:14:21.039 --> 00:14:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not really buying into it</b></Default>

00:14:23.330 --> 00:14:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of dream
did you have, Fukuyama.</b></Default>

00:14:25.659 --> 00:14:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, I was back in Hokkaido
or something.</b></Default>

00:14:28.120 --> 00:14:29.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why Hokkaido?</b></Default>

00:14:29.450 --> 00:14:30.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm from there.</b></Default>

00:14:30.659 --> 00:14:32.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the first time
I'm hearing of this.</b></Default>

00:14:32.370 --> 00:14:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you that
when I introduced myself.</b></Default>

00:14:34.830 --> 00:14:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also, I told you my birthday
is on the 30th of this month.</b></Default>

00:14:37.830 --> 00:14:39.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First time I'm hearing that too.</b></Default>

00:14:39.750 --> 00:14:42.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or rather, is it common
for people from Hokkaido</b></Default>

00:14:42.409 --> 00:14:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to come to our university?</b></Default>

00:14:44.250 --> 00:14:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is that?</b></Default>

00:14:45.370 --> 00:14:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I recently got to know
another student from Hokkaido.</b></Default>

00:14:48.580 --> 00:14:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Knowing you, Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:51.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's got to be
a really cute girl.</b></Default>

00:14:51.750 --> 00:14:52.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So can you introduce me?</b></Default>

00:14:53.370 --> 00:14:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, Fukuyama, why did you
choose our university?</b></Default>

00:14:56.450 --> 00:14:58.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, don't try to change
the subject so obviously.</b></Default>

00:14:58.909 --> 00:15:00.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This girl must be pretty cute
if you...</b></Default>

00:15:01.450 --> 00:15:02.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:15:05.120 --> 00:15:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

00:15:06.700 --> 00:15:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come to think</b></Default>

00:15:08.159 --> 00:15:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why did I choose to apply
for this university</b></Default>

00:15:10.330 --> 00:15:11.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the first place?</b></Default>

00:15:14.580 --> 00:15:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scribbling]</b></Default>

00:15:25.539 --> 00:15:27.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to have a talk.</b></Default>

00:15:29.659 --> 00:15:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MIDDLE OF AN EXAM RIGHT NOW</b></Default>

00:15:32.200 --> 00:15:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll just wait right here
until you're done.</b></Default>

00:15:41.080 --> 00:15:42.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excuse me.</b></Default>

00:15:42.250 --> 00:15:45.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My stomach's upset, so I'm
going to go to the bathroom.</b></Default>

00:15:56.289 --> 00:15:57.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmph.</b></Default>

00:15:58.159 --> 00:15:59.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:16:01.450 --> 00:16:02.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>All right. Spill.</i></b></Default>

00:16:02.950 --> 00:16:04.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>What do you want from me now?</i></b></Default>

00:16:04.659 --> 00:16:06.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just what does your girlfriend
think she's up to?</b></Default>

00:16:06.950 --> 00:16:08.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's up to something?</b></Default>

00:16:08.409 --> 00:16:10.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are they saying online
she's Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If their posts
are really bothering you</b></Default>

00:16:13.080 --> 00:16:14.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you could prove them wrong</b></Default>

00:16:14.159 --> 00:16:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by announcing, "I'm the real
Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:16:17.039 --> 00:16:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You could even stream right now
and clear things up.</b></Default>

00:16:19.080 --> 00:16:20.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It won't work.</b></Default>

00:16:20.250 --> 00:16:23.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any video footage with my face
is invisible to everyone.</b></Default>

00:16:23.580 --> 00:16:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only thing people can see
are views from behind</b></Default>

00:16:26.080 --> 00:16:27.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I film from a distance.</b></Default>

00:16:27.370 --> 00:16:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, okay then.</b></Default>

00:16:28.659 --> 00:16:31.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you need to be perceived
by others before the reveal.</b></Default>

00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't have any ideas
why this happened, Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't.</b></Default>

00:16:36.370 --> 00:16:38.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iwamizawa doesn't have
any ideas either?</b></Default>

00:16:40.080 --> 00:16:41.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like
there's something there.</b></Default>

00:16:41.700 --> 00:16:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This would all be resolved</b></Default>

00:16:42.830 --> 00:16:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if your girlfriend
simply denies it.</b></Default>

00:16:44.700 --> 00:16:46.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can make that happen, right?</b></Default>

00:16:46.250 --> 00:16:47.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I can do something
about this</b></Default>

00:16:48.039 --> 00:16:50.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will I receive a reward
in return?</b></Default>

00:16:50.289 --> 00:16:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

00:16:52.080 --> 00:16:54.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll go on a date
with you for a day.</b></Default>

00:16:54.830 --> 00:16:55.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Very well.</b></Default>

00:16:56.250 --> 00:16:57.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do what I can.</b></Default>

00:17:02.330 --> 00:17:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess we have a deal.</b></Default>

00:17:06.700 --> 00:17:08.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'm counting on you.</b></Default>

00:17:09.539 --> 00:17:10.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way</b></Default>

00:17:10.700 --> 00:17:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>did you see any dreams
on Christmas, Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:17:13.579 --> 00:17:15.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't have any dreams
that night.</b></Default>

00:17:15.619 --> 00:17:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Interesting. Neither did Mai.</b></Default>

00:17:21.789 --> 00:17:23.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] Welcome back</b></Default>

00:17:24.250 --> 00:17:26.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds like one of those
weird titles on a morning drama.</b></Default>

00:17:27.039 --> 00:17:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone in our basic seminar
hurried up and left.</b></Default>

00:17:30.079 --> 00:17:32.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently they have
a New Year's party to go to.</b></Default>

00:17:32.700 --> 00:17:34.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why didn't you
go along with them, Mito?</b></Default>

00:17:34.869 --> 00:17:36.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, there's something
I wanted to ask you</b></Default>

00:17:37.000 --> 00:17:38.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's more important.</b></Default>

00:17:38.200 --> 00:17:39.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you asking for my type?</b></Default>

00:17:39.700 --> 00:17:41.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, that'd be Mai, of course.</b></Default>

00:17:41.289 --> 00:17:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I know that</b></Default>

00:17:42.329 --> 00:17:44.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but then, who was the woman
you left the room with earlier?</b></Default>

00:17:44.950 --> 00:17:45.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

00:17:45.950 --> 00:17:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She dresses up
like a miniskirt Santa</b></Default>

00:17:47.750 --> 00:17:49.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>every so often, doesn't she?</b></Default>

00:17:49.869 --> 00:17:51.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're able to see her?</b></Default>

00:17:51.910 --> 00:17:52.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:17:54.369 --> 00:17:57.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, I think
I get the gist of it now.</b></Default>

00:17:57.079 --> 00:17:59.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that's why Manami gave me
a weird look the other day</b></Default>

00:17:59.829 --> 00:18:01.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when I told her</b></Default>

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:04.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In reality, it's not that
she's actually invisible</b></Default>

00:18:04.750 --> 00:18:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but more like nobody
outside of you and me</b></Default>

00:18:06.829 --> 00:18:08.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are able to perceive her.</b></Default>

00:18:08.250 --> 00:18:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Same for
the Miss Campus website.</b></Default>

00:18:10.250 --> 00:18:12.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The page detailing the winner</b></Default>

00:18:12.869 --> 00:18:14.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is invisible to others.</b></Default>

00:18:14.410 --> 00:18:16.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think I'd be able to see it?</b></Default>

00:18:17.119 --> 00:18:19.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whoa, you carry that around
every day?</b></Default>

00:18:19.750 --> 00:18:22.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A gentleman should never peek
at a maiden's laptop.</b></Default>

00:18:22.750 --> 00:18:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, so there must be some
obscene files hidden on there.</b></Default>

00:18:25.829 --> 00:18:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah. Totally.</b></Default>

00:18:27.619 --> 00:18:29.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[typing]</b></Default>

00:18:29.119 --> 00:18:30.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, this one?</b></Default>

00:18:30.619 --> 00:18:32.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Last year's grand prize.</b></Default>

00:18:32.539 --> 00:18:33.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NENE IWAMIZAWA: SOPHOMORE
MAJOR: INTERNATIONAL EDUCATION</b></Default>

00:18:33.539 --> 00:18:35.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sophomore
in International Education</b></Default>

00:18:35.500 --> 00:18:37.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>originally from Hokkaido.</b></Default>

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:38.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] That's the one.</b></Default>

00:18:39.039 --> 00:18:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI]
She's on social media, too.</b></Default>

00:18:41.579 --> 00:18:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does she look like
she'd have a reason</b></Default>

00:18:43.329 --> 00:18:44.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to make her want to disappear?</b></Default>

00:18:44.910 --> 00:18:47.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like
she stopped posting in April</b></Default>

00:18:47.160 --> 00:18:49.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so maybe something happened
around that time?</b></Default>

00:18:49.200 --> 00:18:50.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For instance?</b></Default>

00:18:50.200 --> 00:18:52.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe Mai came back
from her leave of absence</b></Default>

00:18:52.700 --> 00:18:54.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and showed up at the university</b></Default>

00:18:54.410 --> 00:18:56.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she instantly stole
everyone's attention</b></Default>

00:18:56.410 --> 00:18:59.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>away from her</b></Default>

00:18:59.200 --> 00:19:00.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, maybe.</b></Default>

00:19:00.619 --> 00:19:02.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This girl is a model
and the grand prize winner</b></Default>

00:19:02.789 --> 00:19:04.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of a Miss Campus contest.</b></Default>

00:19:04.200 --> 00:19:05.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure
before Mai showed up here</b></Default>

00:19:05.910 --> 00:19:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was being flattered
all over campus.</b></Default>

00:19:08.329 --> 00:19:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai was like an intruder</b></Default>

00:19:10.039 --> 00:19:11.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and this campus was the kingdom</b></Default>

00:19:11.700 --> 00:19:14.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Princess Nene Iwamizawa
was ruling before her.</b></Default>

00:19:14.750 --> 00:19:17.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But then famed actress
Queen Mai Sakurajima</b></Default>

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:20.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>stormed into the kingdom
and usurped the throne.</b></Default>

00:19:20.369 --> 00:19:22.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you're forced
to go up against Mai</b></Default>

00:19:22.410 --> 00:19:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>falling into ruin
in an instant is a given.</b></Default>

00:19:24.789 --> 00:19:27.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe her beautiful tiara
and dress were stripped away</b></Default>

00:19:27.539 --> 00:19:28.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she dropped ranks</b></Default>

00:19:28.539 --> 00:19:30.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all the way down
to a lowly commoner.</b></Default>

00:19:30.829 --> 00:19:33.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why
Nene Iwamizawa disappeared.</b></Default>

00:19:34.289 --> 00:19:37.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because her value wasn't
being acknowledged anymore.</b></Default>

00:19:37.119 --> 00:19:38.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:19:38.450 --> 00:19:40.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's slightly different
from that, though.</b></Default>

00:19:40.539 --> 00:19:42.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hmm?
-Due to Mai showing up</b></Default>

00:19:42.450 --> 00:19:44.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was no longer seen
as someone who was special.</b></Default>

00:19:44.700 --> 00:19:47.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she came to realize that
all of her so-called friends</b></Default>

00:19:47.500 --> 00:19:48.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that constantly surrounded her</b></Default>

00:19:48.750 --> 00:19:50.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were now laughing
behind her back.</b></Default>

00:19:50.500 --> 00:19:53.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So perhaps she felt miserable
and went into hiding.</b></Default>

00:19:53.200 --> 00:19:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:19:54.329 --> 00:19:56.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone asserting dominance
being taken down a peg</b></Default>

00:19:56.750 --> 00:19:59.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>makes you think, "Ha-ha!
Serves you right</b></Default>

00:20:00.289 --> 00:20:02.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess so.</b></Default>

00:20:02.289 --> 00:20:04.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And on top of
all that complicated stuff</b></Default>

00:20:04.950 --> 00:20:07.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so-called hurt people think
they aren't hurting anyone else.</b></Default>

00:20:07.910 --> 00:20:10.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, that, or they think
it's perfectly okay</b></Default>

00:20:10.539 --> 00:20:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for them to hurt others.</b></Default>

00:20:12.119 --> 00:20:15.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As if it was a privilege
that they earned.</b></Default>

00:20:16.289 --> 00:20:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something happen to you
in the past, Mito?</b></Default>

00:20:18.660 --> 00:20:19.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something?</b></Default>

00:20:19.750 --> 00:20:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems as though you were
speaking from experience.</b></Default>

00:20:22.329 --> 00:20:24.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, of course
I have a thing or two</b></Default>

00:20:24.160 --> 00:20:26.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that happened to me in the past</b></Default>

00:20:26.869 --> 00:20:27.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you see</b></Default>

00:20:28.000 --> 00:20:30.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this girl is Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:20:30.119 --> 00:20:32.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With her reputation</b></Default>

00:20:32.539 --> 00:20:35.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as much as she wants by saying</b></Default>

00:20:35.250 --> 00:20:36.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if she desired.</b></Default>

00:20:36.289 --> 00:20:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case, maybe she's not
actually Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:20:40.500 --> 00:20:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:20:42.410 --> 00:20:43.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] This friend of yours
sure says</b></Default>

00:20:43.950 --> 00:20:45.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>some of
the most interesting things.</b></Default>

00:20:45.539 --> 00:20:46.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Though</b></Default>

00:20:46.660 --> 00:20:48.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm still
just a potential friend.</b></Default>

00:20:48.250 --> 00:20:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 7TH</b></Default>

00:20:49.289 --> 00:20:51.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what's your take
on this, Futaba?</b></Default>

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do think what she said
is a probable deduction</b></Default>

00:20:53.579 --> 00:20:55.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of what led up to the situation.</b></Default>

00:20:55.369 --> 00:20:56.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, it is.</b></Default>

00:20:56.910 --> 00:20:58.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Personally, though</b></Default>

00:20:58.450 --> 00:21:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I'm more concerned
about that misunderstanding</b></Default>

00:21:00.789 --> 00:21:02.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about Sakurajima right now.</b></Default>

00:21:02.700 --> 00:21:04.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're talking about it
as if it were the truth</b></Default>

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:06.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over at my university.</b></Default>

00:21:06.500 --> 00:21:09.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That Sakurajima
really is Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:21:09.619 --> 00:21:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think that will be resolved
the day after tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:21:13.250 --> 00:21:14.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The holiday?</b></Default>

00:21:14.789 --> 00:21:15.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. You know</b></Default>

00:21:15.910 --> 00:21:18.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it'll be Coming of Age Day</b></Default>

00:21:19.039 --> 00:21:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the Coming of Age
Ceremony interview.</b></Default>

00:21:21.410 --> 00:21:22.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll just deny it</b></Default>

00:21:22.450 --> 00:21:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and post the same thing
on her social media.</b></Default>

00:21:25.119 --> 00:21:26.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, my only concern</b></Default>

00:21:26.869 --> 00:21:28.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would be if the rumors
don't die down</b></Default>

00:21:28.750 --> 00:21:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even after doing all that.</b></Default>

00:21:30.500 --> 00:21:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] It is possible
that the people</b></Default>

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who had the same dream</b></Default>

00:21:33.329 --> 00:21:35.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>might believe in that
more than her statements.</b></Default>

00:21:35.950 --> 00:21:37.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way</b></Default>

00:21:37.410 --> 00:21:40.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what kind of dream did you have
on Christmas Eve, Futaba?</b></Default>

00:21:40.579 --> 00:21:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was going out with Kunimi.</b></Default>

00:21:42.329 --> 00:21:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:21:43.329 --> 00:21:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. We were eating together.</b></Default>

00:21:45.329 --> 00:21:46.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I think it was a date.</b></Default>

00:21:46.910 --> 00:21:47.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For real?</b></Default>

00:21:48.289 --> 00:21:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that's impossible.</b></Default>

00:21:50.079 --> 00:21:51.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kunimi, of all people.</b></Default>

00:21:52.829 --> 00:21:55.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After the bit with Kasai</b></Default>

00:21:55.829 --> 00:21:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:21:57.329 --> 00:21:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not being able to reciprocate
someone's feelings</b></Default>

00:22:00.039 --> 00:22:01.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can often be stifling.</b></Default>

00:22:03.079 --> 00:22:05.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if Kunimi
felt the same way.</b></Default>

00:22:08.000 --> 00:22:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still, though</b></Default>

00:22:09.329 --> 00:22:11.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't believe that dream
was actually the future.</b></Default>

00:22:12.500 --> 00:22:14.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're saying that</b></Default>

00:22:15.450 --> 00:22:17.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi said so too</b></Default>

00:22:17.539 --> 00:22:20.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that perhaps that dream
wasn't looking into the future</b></Default>

00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:23.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it was more like peeking
into the other possible universe</b></Default>

00:22:23.750 --> 00:22:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from this one.</b></Default>

00:22:25.910 --> 00:22:27.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, even so</b></Default>

00:22:27.500 --> 00:22:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's like, what can we even do
about it at this point?</b></Default>

